Vitamin E is well known for its miraculous effects on the skin and the nails. It has an incredible effect on the skin against premature ageing. You can prevent your nails from becoming dull and brittle by the continuous use of the Vitamin E Nail and Cuticle Oil from Sally Hansen. The unique formula of this Nail and Cuticle Oil absorbs quickly in to the nails and cuticles and provides deep hydration to them instantly.
